f50f852bf9aab8e759504ba6f724920d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F14%2F233547_f50f852bf9aab8e759504ba6f724920d.gif&h=44cdcd3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/15/185308_aad906a54864ad5e19c4c7c30c6216d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F15%2F185308_aad906a54864ad5e19c4c7c30c6216d2.gif&h=b1ff0dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主題曲：星野 源 - 「恋」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jhOVibLEDhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjhOVibLEDhA&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=62996c34\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jhOVibLEDhA</a><br />\n恋ダンス 教學片<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMOyGxzG91yo&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=fdaba7bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CsPUakUVMAEaIm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCsPUakUVMAEaIm9.jpg&h=ff57ed82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CufWpTsXgAE8r5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCufWpTsXgAE8r5D.jpg&h=e6f7af0b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n　　女星新垣結衣接拍十月開播TBS日劇《逃避雖可恥但有用》，飾演像上班一樣為特定目的結婚的新妻，劇集根據海野津波在月刊《Kiss》連載的同名漫畫改編，以&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的價值觀為基礎，講述契約結婚的主人公的故事。<br />\n<br />\n　　劇中新垣結衣飾演主人公森山，這位25歲愛妄想的女子沒有男友，畢業後沒有工作，做派遣職員沒公司用，生活不順終日煩惱，她幫單身職員津崎做家務，對方提出不如像上班一樣結婚，於是他們秘密定下契約，開始了&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的新婚生活。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>分析文(含劇透)<br />\n《逃恥》：厭世地擁抱生命中的缺憾</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/59675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F59675&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=ff5645f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/59675</a><br />\n<br />\n《逃恥》橫掃91回學院賞<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/h2TnKc2.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh2TnKc2.png&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=378dcb11\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/h2TnKc2.png</a>"},{"pid":"b1021f6dacc20bbd49e40725c2a356eec40b70df","tid":139317,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ccd3d2d003b0f04669b31eee2ad5d46444be46","tid":139317,"uid":51944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c8d3c4b9dca9c6ed86d0fe8ec272ddbffa7abb","tid":139317,"uid":33872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"支持下你啦"},{"pid":"2910b45192f79e74037303201453681a94d75355","tid":139317,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i8fjks5y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi8fjks5y&h=b1f8934a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5gld0z4w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5gld0z4w&h=d0852bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3049cig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3049cig.jpg&h=d1466154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39623b35c1d9c66baa790e040cefe1d42eb1702","tid":139317,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88404fabe71cb220c7946f9359